c6185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWxRo2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWxRo2R.jpg&h=1a7a9910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3932a80b869bb538fc729ef03c88fe96314089f2","tid":1744664,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:57:54.000Z","msg":"18-11-2019 (原片）香港警察踩示威者頭部<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你好我係拍片嘅本人，有冇人知道個手足點樣？可以幫手retweet 比多啲人睇到,想推到出國際記者報道，謝謝 Twitter link <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Ng18607704/status/1196632031314137094\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNg18607704%2Fstatus%2F1196632031314137094&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt8%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=015bebe8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNg18607704%2Fstatus%2F1196632031314137094&h=20f75937\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Ng18607704/status/1196632031314137094</a>"}]}